A demon lady of the Abyss, Pale Night is an ancient entity of unspeakable power, an Obyrith said to be the mother of numerous princes, including such figures as Lupercio, Graz'zt, Rhyxali, and Vucarik of Chains.
In recent millennia, she has kept a tower of bone in the endless maze of Baphomet. 

      Sources:&nbsp;
    
            
                    Faces of Evil: The Fiends        
              
                    Fiendish Codex I: Hordes of the Abyss